overview: Swingers, Ordinary people who hook up for sex. Are they your neighbors? You'll be shocked and delighted when Fallen Angel exposes the Swingers Date Club contest, sponsored by Adam & Eve, held at the Trapeze Club in Atlanta, Ga. Lovin' the southland, XXX stars Alexandra Silk and Holly Hollywood judge the "Miss SDC - USA" pageant. This sexually charged extravaganza was easily won by Gwenn. Her prize? To be our new starlet-in-training! See Gwenn flown to L. A. introduced to superstar Carmen Luvana and swept away by a huge swinger's orgy. It's quite a make-over!
title: Swinging In The USA
